\begin{abstract} A four-parameter class of exact asymptotically flat
solutions of the Einstein-Maxwell equations involving only rational
functions is presented.  It is able to describe the exterior field of
a slowly or rapidly rotating neutron star with poloidal magnetic
field.
\end{abstract}

